title: Bosch Benchmark Series Double Oven HBLP651 Overview
description:
Buy Bosch Benchmark Series Double Wall Oven HBLP651 - http://www.abt.com/resources/pages/search.php?keywords=hblp651

Key Features:
• Side-Opening Door Offers Better Ergonomic Access to the Oven Cavity.
• A Full-Extension Telescopic Rack Offers Safe Access To The Oven Cavity.
• Bosch Wall Ovens are Compatible with Most Competitors Cutouts.
• The Color TFT Control Panel with SteelTouch™ Buttons is Easy to Use.
• The Wall Oven is Designed to be Installed Flush with your Cabinetry.
Features:
• Design: Color TFT Touch Control with SteelTouch™ Buttons for Easier Operation of the Oven
• Performance:
o 14 Specialized Cooking Modes in Both Cavities - Gourmet Cooking Made Easy
o Custom Cooking Programs Both Cavities: No-Preheat Frozen Food Mode Pizza Pie Warm and Proof
o Genuine European Convection in Both Cavities
o Temperature Conversion for Convection Cooking
o Fast Preheat Reduces Preheat Time
• Efficiency:
o EcoClean™ 2-Hour Self-Clean Cycle
o EcoChef Mode - Remaing Heat in Cavity Finishes Cooking Process
• Covenience:
o AutoProbe: Takes the Guesswork out of Rare Medium and Well Don
o Two Halogen Lights per Cavity Provide Superior Illumination
o Timer with Cook Time and Delay Start Function
o Extra Large Door Window for Easy Monitoring of Cooking Process
o Star-K certified. F100°-450°. Two Separate Time Intervals can be Programmed
• Capacity:
o Large Capacity at 4.6 Cu Ft.
o Recessed 8 Pass Broil Element for Increased Capacity and Safety
